divs: Sighting Detailssince july last year my partner and i have been watching the skys because we saw a triangular ufo with three bright red lights,every time the sky is clear,stars visible we spend time looking in case we see another one.yesterday and today we saw an object that looked like a star,no flashing lights just moving past until on both occasions it disapeared.neither of us could say for sure what they were.it got cold so i came in and went upstairs to look out our bed room window,after about half an hour to my amazement i saw what apeared to be a dark shape,no lights on,that would be discribed as boomerang.not at all like the triangle i had seen before,it passed over like a shadow,quite low,it was larger than anything i have ever seen before,it had small circular shapes underneath all the way along it on either side it all happened so quick ijust watched it glide by.i am not afraid yet i am still exited and shocked all at the same time.craft silent.
